itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway discuss the latest college football Playoff Poll in real time, as well as break down their picks for this week's NFL games, Championship Week in college, and the winner of the Wilder/Fury fight.  Also, Mat Best, Jarred Taylor, and Evan Hafer will be doing a live podcast from the Army/Navy game in Philly next Saturday!
